description: A chemical laboratory simulation app for Android A chemical laboratory simulation app for Android This is a fork of ChemistryLab by Trần Thanh Tùng. The functionality has not changed, only the user interface. Changes: - Translated app to English (& added support for other languages) - Added English literature - Migrated to AndroidX, RTL-Support & Upgraded Libraries - App does now support different screen dpis - Bugfixes
